File: install.rb
Desc:  Install the acme service.  
For help: 
ruby install.rb --help

File: acme
Desc: init.d script for RedHat linux.  
Note: You need to edit the script and replace the hard coded 
      default dir (/usr/local/acme) if you target install acme
      in another directory (ruby install.rb -t <dir>).
To Install:
cp acme /etc/init.d/acme
chkconfig --add acme
